br />\n咪係<br />\n呢到入面大把<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【含J圖】【生日快樂】我 又 大 一 歲 啦 打 返 個 J 先~~~~<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/497437/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/497437/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d0e8abe2a5f82d28517be16b1716d4034f45dcf6","tid":497690,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T06:09:20.000Z","msg":"醫心臟病？"},{"pid":"003e6cf2871d0198978ed4f741d4aa042f2f0fc2","tid":497690,"uid":53351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T06:16:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真是一個好地方！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好條撚 有女先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73987622ebd4d24f3f5e26effee4e2bd2bcc13f8","tid":497690,"uid":25231,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T06:19:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醫心臟病？</blockquote><br />\n原先隻藥做臨床test 係想醫心臟病<br />\n後尾成效唔大<br />\n最後要測試者交返D藥出黎<br />\n但冇一個願意<br />\n之後就發現原來有壯陽功效<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"e02d63fb29a8697d99135a2aeccb0f5dac9b62a9","tid":497690,"uid":87428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T06:24:22.000Z","msg":"竟然沒 口吸版"},{"pid":"083a4f6d1cf26cd2eeff7b436bfa7622b1619cb0","tid":497690,"uid":89394,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T06:24:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>醫心臟病？</blockquote><br />\n原先隻藥做臨床test 係想醫心臟病<br />\n後尾成效唔大<br />\n最後要測試者交返D藥出黎<br />\n但冇一個願意<br />\n之後就發現原來有壯陽功效<br />\n好似係</blockquote><br />\n西地那非由美國輝瑞製藥公司在英國肯特郡桑威治的研究中心研發，本是為了用於治療心血管疾病的5-磷酸二酯酶抑制藥而進入臨床試驗的。研究者希望西地那非能夠透過釋放生物活性物質一氧化氮以舒張心血管平滑肌，來達到擴張血管緩解心血管疾病的目的。但是在斯旺西莫里森醫院的第一場臨床試驗顯示，西地那非對心血管的作用並不能達到研究人員的預期，其用於心血管藥物的表現令人失望，無法成為成功的治療藥物。[1]<br />\n<br />\n1991年4月，西地那非的臨床研究正式宣告失敗，但受試者報告的一項副作用引起了研究人員的注意。研究員發現，治療者在領過試藥之後都不願意交出餘下的藥物。追查之下，發現這一種藥對病者的性生活有改善。在經輝瑞高層許可後，研究人員就西地那非對陰莖海綿體平滑肌的作用展開了研究，並於1998年3月27日獲得美國聯邦食品和藥品管理局的上市許可[2]，之後迅速獲得商業上的成功，2008年輝瑞公司藉此獲利19.34億美元[3]，成為令該公司名聲大噪的一個產品[4]。"},{"pid":"a4441e8147f57bccf7a4b83545f582397b4cf947","tid":497690,"uid":25231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T06:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>竟然沒 口吸版</blockquote><br />\n應該好似哮喘藥咁<br />\n一拎出黎噴一噴<br />\n快過食藥"},{"pid":"2a1ab7d0a6c5d3ff67d17ebbcc42170fbb3b4e3a","tid":497690,"uid":14605,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T06:51:08.000Z","msg":"今晚搬去住"},{"pid":"5e20d5a4a4c53d8e0badff654e75c70220beae7d","tid":497690,"uid":59678,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T06:52:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今晚搬去住</blockquote><br />\n你個名同你句野又幾夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f867bfcffa7c6e3043a31abeb13e84d19a17ce5","tid":497690,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T06:55:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">方</span></span>"},{"pid":"99f5a2c54769680422fdab6508dfb519f087f9b8","tid":497690,"uid":99805,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T06:56:16.000Z","msg":"青頭唔明白<br />\n硬唔代表有性慾"},{"pid":"0e540917ef39a9858199a54308e9ab3a5cbfa649","tid":497690,"uid":52591,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T07:03:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>青頭唔明白<br />\n硬唔代表有性慾</blockquote><br />\n有性慾唔代表硬呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75d43cfc319e8c51214131ac21e0ade0165eb8e","tid":497690,"uid":65443,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T08:09:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171209/640_ce3b80b036a728a0737